QuestData.Title: Return to Sha'tari Base Camp
QuestData.Description: We will not make it back on our own. The dreadfang poison is too strong. You must return to Sha'tari Base Camp for us. Scout Navrin will send a rescue party out to find us.
QuestData.LogDescription: Vindicator Haylen wants you to return to the Sha'tari Base Camp in the Bone Wastes and speak with Scout Navrin.
QuestData.RewardText: It is good to know that some of our warriors fought well against the dreadfang widows. We will send a rescue party immediately.
